{
  "stem": "25639.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of this, we inherited on both sides-- my mother's side and my father's side of the families.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some of it, my dad purchased.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I have a little list which my father gave me in which he-- he wrote himself-- in which he very interestingly names all the fields that we had.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And until then, I could only remember first seven, then 14, and then I knew there was more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't-- and later my dad was able to write down every one of them and how big they-- the size of the fields, and how he obtained them, how he purchased them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That, that one was because someone couldn't pay the mortgage and the bank had to take it over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it went up for sale, and anybody could buy it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And here my dad saved money in order to purchase more and more land so that we can grow, along with the size of the family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that my parents and grandparents were born in this town, so far as I know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But beyond that I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- this would take me to about the middle of the 19th century, 18-- maybe 1840, 1850.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1944, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the anti-Semitism reached its climax.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German-- I'd like to go back a step.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the Hungarians took over in 1938, the Hungarians continued the anti-Semitic laws that, that were put into effect in Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They filtered down into the German occupied areas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, it filtered down into our town, and that's what I am here to report about.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so the drummer would come, and he'd stop at the corners of the streets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people would drop everything they were doing to listen to the news.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
